data.description:
***** Price Reduction ***** A little TLC finish Or Investor opportunity. Great, freshly painted Ranch with 3 Bedrooms & Bonus room for Office or Play room. Newly renovated Bathroom in progress. Large eat-in Kitchen includes built-in microwave and gas cooking stove. Living/ Dining Room combo has lots of light and large window. Large bedrooms, 2 of them have new carpeting and new windows. Some glass block windows for privacy. Full basement with rec room. Backs to school athletic field with large open space.  Great quiet location.

*To be sold as/is, Inspections or informational purposes only. Seller to do no repairs for Inspections, including Municipal or occupancy.*
